  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK803">
<l>paḻakiya naṭpevaṉ ceyyuṅ keḻutakaimai</l>
<l>ceytāṅ kamaiyāk kaṭai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Of what avail is long-standing friendship, if friends do not admit as their own actions done through the right of intimacy ?</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
